Egypt Travel Recommendations:
1. Stay @fscaironp! Use the concierge to book excursions with private tour guides and take advantage of their private limousines (Mercedes and a nice @mercedesmaybach !) to get you around. It’s a very safe way to go and about 1/3 the price of a typical stay in New York City!
2. Visit the Giza necropolis to view the pyramids, the Sphinx, take a camel ride and go inside the pyramids!
3. Take a @nilemaximcruising dinner cruise on the Nile for good food, live entertainment and belly dancing by @allavats_official 
4. Visit the Khan el-Khalili a famous shopping bazaar and souk in the historic center of Cairo!
5.  Visit the @egyptian.museum!
6.  What are your favorites?

3010 Paseo Tranquillo, Santa Barbara, CA 93105 $4,250,000 4/2.5 plus charming “ADU” studio!

This Instagram-worthy Coastal Modern Farmhouse and charming cottage are regarded as two of the most beautiful homes in California! Designed in collaboration with multiple award-winning architectural and interior design firm AB design studio, this stunning single level home features a warm, modern interior design with a board and batten beach house exterior, providing unmatched luxury. Walls disappear, connecting indoor and outdoor sanctuary spaces through 4 sets of panoramic folding doors. The landscape design is inviting and beyond beautiful, featuring a covered outdoor living room, approximately 680sf modern redwood deck, modern fire-pit lawns and olive trees. Surrounded by privacy hedges, white roses and lavender, outdoor living spaces are as equally stunning as the finely crafted interiors. Entering the home through its custom Dutch doors, you will find an art gallery and a completely open floor plan with a modern fireplace. The master suite is ultra-luxurious with high ceilings, walk-in closets with Louis Vuitton & Hermes backlit display and a seamless connection to an outdoor lounge. The spa-like master bath features a deep soaking modern tub, his and hers sinks and dual rain shower heads in his and hers custom shower. Totally remodeled inside and out with everything essentially new, additional high-end amenities include blazing-speed Fiber optic internet, air-conditioning, Nest, Lutron Caseta lighting system, Sonos whole house audio, high-end appliances and much, much more. Discover the good life and make this your modern oasis.
